  "Aftersales Pairing : ESCL": {
   "width": 11340,
   "height": 9180,
   "color": "rgb(130,125,47)",
   "labels": [
    {
     "text": "Protected Pairing : Electrical Steering Column Locked pairing in After Sales ",
     "color": "rgb(237,249,11)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(64,0,64)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 0,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 11040
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Procedure : ",
     "color": "rgb(242,245,118)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 480,
      "height": 6720,
      "width": 11040
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "2) Check that the BCM is not blank and the ESCL is blank (try to start the vehicle) and read the ESCL information \"SteeringLock Blanck/coded\"",
     "color": "rgb(242,245,118)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 1200,
      "height": 480,
      "width": 11040
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "3) Press the button \"Request ESCL pairing\"",
     "color": "rgb(242,245,118)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 1560,
      "height": 225,
      "width": 9909
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "4) Select the \"Input Data to Server\" (19 bytes) and copy it in the application \"Pairing using DDT2000\".  ",
     "color": "rgb(242,245,118)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(15,15,15)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 2040,
      "height": 285,
      "width": 9875
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "5) Complete the frames in the application and press the button \"Calcul\".Get the \"Server answer\" (16 bytes) and copy it in this screen. Then press the button \"Transmit Server Answer\" ",
     "color": "rgb(242,245,118)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 137,
      "top": 2655,
      "height": 615,
      "width": 11023
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "6) If the BCM is SA unlocked for ESCL pairing, then put the Ignition OFF, select \"startRoutine\" and press the button \"Authorize ESCL pairing\" ",
     "color": "rgb(242,245,118)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 4560,
      "height": 240,
      "width": 10560
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "7) If the authorization to pair is ok, then put the Ignition ON. If the ESCL is paired ( \"blank_coded = false\") the exit of the procedure is automatic.",
     "color": "rgb(242,245,118)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 6360,
      "height": 405,
      "width": 10785
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "ESCL / BCM information",
     "color": "rgb(240,236,179)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 5640,
      "top": 7320,
      "height": 1800,
      "width": 5520
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "SA failure ",
     "color": "rgb(240,236,179)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 7320,
      "height": 1800,
      "width": 5400
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "8) To postpone the authorization to pair the ESCL, press the button ",
     "color": "rgb(242,245,118)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 6840,
      "height": 240,
      "width": 6600
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "1) !! Check that you have access rights to the application \"Pairing using DDT2000\"",
     "color": "rgb(242,245,118)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(15,15,15)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 840,
      "height": 240,
      "width": 11040
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
