      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "6) If the BCM is SA unlocked for ECM pairing then put the Ignition Power Supply OFF, select \"startRoutine\" and press the button \"Authorize ECM pairing\" ",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
