  "Aftersales Pairing : MG": {
   "width": 11940,
   "height": 9780,
   "color": "rgb(128,0,0)",
   "labels": [
    {
     "text": "MG After Sales Protected Pairing",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(15,15,15)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 120,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 11745
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Procedure : ",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 600,
      "height": 6480,
      "width": 11730
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "2) Check that the MG is blank (try to start the vehicle) and read the MG information \" MG_IS_BLANK\"",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 1320,
      "height": 285,
      "width": 8775
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "3) Press the button \"Request Server MG pairing\"",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 1680,
      "height": 300,
      "width": 8790
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "4) Select the \"Input Data to Server\" (19 bytes) and copy it in the application \"Pairing using DDT2000\".  ",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 2040,
      "height": 255,
      "width": 8775
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "5) Complete the frames in the application and press the button \"Calcul\".Get the \"Server answer\" (16 bytes) and copy it in this screen. Then press the button \"Transmit Server Answer\" ",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 2880,
      "height": 615,
      "width": 8760
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "1) !! Check that you have access rights to the application \"Pairing using DDT2000\"",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 840,
      "height": 480,
      "width": 10020
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "6) If the BCM is SA unlocked for MG pairing then put the Ignition Power Supply OFF, select \"startRoutine\" and press the button \"Authorize MG pairing\" ",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 4800,
      "height": 885,
      "width": 11520
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "7) If the authorization to pair is TRUE, then switch Ignition Power Supply ON. If the ECM is paired, procedure exit is automatic.",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 6360,
      "height": 405,
      "width": 10080
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "MG / BCM information",
     "color": "rgb(240,236,179)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 6120,
      "top": 7200,
      "height": 2520,
      "width": 5760
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "SA failure ",
     "color": "rgb(240,236,179)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 7200,
      "height": 2520,
      "width": 5880
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "8) To postpone the authorization to pair the MG, press the button ",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 6720,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 8760
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "return code",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 2520,
      "top": 5520,
      "height": 300,
      "width": 960
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial Narrow",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "SA Unlocked for MG pairing",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 945,
      "top": 4365,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 3495
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 11.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Authorization to pair MG",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 990,
      "top": 5940,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 3495
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 11.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "::pic:misc\\warning_32x32",
     "color": "rgb(255,0,0)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
